fields.Title: You: ""I thought it was an Ace's High mom..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought it was an Ace's High moment, Kim."

fields.Title: Barred Door: "It's barred from the inside. You he..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's barred from the inside. You hear the bar rattle in the brackets.

fields.Title: Barred Door: "This is the door to the pinball wor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is the door to the pinball workshop that you left barred on the inside.

fields.Title: You: ""*Disrespecting* the force?!?!" (Ki..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "*Disrespecting* the force?!?!" (Kick the door.)

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "This kind of stuff would hurt -- if..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This kind of stuff would hurt -- if not for you not caring about little things like that.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Suck on that, door.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Suck on that, door."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""To the workshop behind the wall."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "To the workshop behind the wall." He points somewhere within. "This must be the barred door we saw -- we *could* return and open it from the inside." He looks at the door with suspicion.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "You kick it -- gung ho style, *ente..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You kick it -- gung ho style, *entering the premises* style -- but the door fails to respect the force. All you hear is the bar rattling inside, laughing at you.
fields.Alternate1: You give it another, more *ferocious* kick. The door still does not move.

fields.Title: You: "Swallow the rage."
fields.Dialogue Text: Swallow the rage.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""I think the brackets broke inside...."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think the brackets broke inside. I've always wanted to know what's in there..."

fields.Title: You: ""Where does this lead to?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Where does this lead to?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It is not the first closed door we..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It is not the first closed door we've found in this building -- there is also your mysterious blue kitchen door."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The vigilantes, the cadaver, and....."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The vigilantes, the cadaver, and..." He nods toward the young woman. "A number of people connected to the case are *in* or around this building. This door is part of it. It's not *unimportant*."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Something cracks inside."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something cracks inside.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't know. The further we get,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know. The further we get, the more this building seems to be tied to the case..."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "It is an unbelievably satisfying so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It is an unbelievably satisfying sound.

fields.Title: Shivers: "Below, the hostel-cafeteria creaks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Below, the hostel-cafeteria creaks and groans under your added weight -- a skeleton of composite support beams and cantilevers.

fields.Title: You: "Let's get in there. [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: Let's get in there. [Leave.]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't see how this is going to g..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't see how this is going to give new results." He measures the door, stoically. "There must be another way in there."

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "It could be that your eyesight is s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It could be that your eyesight is still too poor to notice it... behind that window.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "No one knows. It is a fleeting feel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No one knows. It is a fleeting feeling.

fields.Title: Barred Door: "The door receives a thorough discip..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door receives a thorough disciplining.

fields.Title: Barred Door: "This is a small, heavy door. There..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is a small, heavy door. There is no lock in sight.
fields.Alternate1: The same small, heavy door. No lock in sight.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't see how this is going to g..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't see how this is going to give new results." He measures the door, stoically. "There must be another way in there."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Through the kitchen door, perhaps?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Through the kitchen door, perhaps? Let's explore, rather than destroy."

fields.Title: You: ""I thought it was an Ace's Low mome..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I thought it was an Ace's Low moment, Kim."

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""All right," the woman nods approvi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right," the woman nods approvingly: "Let's trash the place."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""No -- still a mini-investigation."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No -- still a mini-investigation." He pretends to make a note in his notebook.

fields.Title: Empathy: "It totally was."
fields.Dialogue Text: It totally was.

fields.Title: Logic: "Must be something valuable inside t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Must be something valuable inside to go through the trouble of protecting it -- the door is very sturdy indeed.

fields.Title: You: "Push."
fields.Dialogue Text: Push.

fields.Title: Half Light: "Your foot is ready to explode and p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your foot is ready to explode and punish this *object*!

fields.Title: You: ""Let's see." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's see." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "Tap on the roof with your foot."
fields.Dialogue Text: Tap on the roof with your foot.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): "The woman takes a drag of her ziggi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The woman takes a drag of her ziggie and nods: "Demolish the place."

fields.Title: You: "What?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What?

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You are a numb, imprecise instrumen..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You are a numb, imprecise instrument to ignore this feeling...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It's the barred door we saw." He l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's the barred door we saw." He looks at the door with suspicion. "I don't know why we didn't open it from the inside -- we *should*."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I hate it when that happens.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I hate it when that happens."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should search downstairs, in th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should search downstairs, in the kitchen -- just in case. Maybe there's a door that leads up, that we don't know of."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Something cracks inside. It is an u..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something cracks inside. It is an unbelievably satisfying sound.
fields.Alternate1: This time -- something cracks inside. It is an unbelievably satisfying sound.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't know about that..." The li..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know about that..." The lieutenant smiles an uncomfortable smile.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Shivers: "A dull thump. Somewhere inside a wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A dull thump. Somewhere inside a wind brace rattles from the imperceptible motion of the building.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "It could be that your eyesight is s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It could be that your eyesight is still too poor to notice it... behind that window.

fields.Title: Barred Door: "The sturdy wood door has lost *all*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The sturdy wood door has lost *all* respect for you.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "Sounds like it's heavy too. Very st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Sounds like it's heavy too. Very sturdy.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I don't know." He makes a note in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I don't know." He makes a note in his notebook.
fields.Alternate1: "I don't know, lieutenant-yefreitor." He makes a note.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Let's not.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Let's not."

fields.Title: Barred Door: "The door receives a thorough discip..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door receives a thorough disciplining -- at the cost of your foot. Your foot hurts. A lot.

fields.Title: You: ""Do you think it's important?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Do you think it's important?"

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Below... in the Union box... was th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Below... in the Union box... was there something behind the window? In the hawthorn branches, brushing against the glass.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "It is an unbelievably satisfying so..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It is an unbelievably satisfying sound.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Its pain and grovelling is much to..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Its pain and grovelling is much to your liking.

fields.Title: Empathy: "She sounds genuinely curious."
fields.Dialogue Text: She sounds genuinely curious.

fields.Title: Klaasje (Miss Oranje Disco Dancer): ""Nice." The young woman nods."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nice." The young woman nods.

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Something cracks inside. It is an u..."

fields.Alternate1: This time -- something cracks inside. It is an unbelievably satisfying sound.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The vigilantes, the cadaver, and....."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The vigilantes, the cadaver, and..." He nods to where they young woman once stood. "A number of people connected to the case are *in* or around this building. This door is part of it. It's not *unimportant*."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Sounds like the property damage wa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sounds like the property damage wasn't in vain, at least. Would it hurt to look in?"
fields.Alternate1: "Well," the lieutenant cups his ear. "Sounds like *this time* the property damage was at least resultive. Would it hurt to look in?"

fields.Title: You: "Kick the door in."
fields.Dialogue Text: Kick the door in.

fields.Title: You: ""See? The main investigation and th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "See? The main investigation and the door below are merging into a *stereo*-investigation."

fields.Title: You: ""I could say something, but I'm not..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I could say something, but I'm not going to, because I don't gloat."

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Filling you with a *belief* in your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Filling you with a *belief* in your own body.

fields.Title: You: "Shake it off."
fields.Dialogue Text: Shake it off.

fields.Title: You: "Ignore the feeling."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ignore the feeling.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""We should search downstairs. There..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We should search downstairs. There are things about this building we don't know yet."

fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "Something cracks inside."
fields.Dialogue Text: Something cracks inside.

fields.Title: You: ""Ow.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Ow."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He doesn't say anything."
fields.Dialogue Text: He doesn't say anything.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The further we get, the more this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The further we get, the more this building seems to be tied to the case..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It must be connected to the room w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It must be connected to the room we found behind the kitchen door. Maybe we should go back and take that elevator up..." He looks at the door with suspicion.

fields.Title: You: ""How?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "How?"
